POST http://localhost:5148/api/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Война и мир",
  "year": 1869,
  "authorId": 1
}

### Create Second Book
POST http://localhost:5148/api/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Преступление и наказание",
  "year": 1866,
  "authorId": 2
}

### Get All Books
GET http://localhost:5148/api/books

### Get Book by ID
GET http://localhost:5148/api/books/1

